Invocation Name: almaden bike club
des:
This skill finds bicycle rides listed by the Almaden Cycle Touring Club in San Jose, CA.

You can find rides by type on a given day.

Ride types can be "billy, grizzly, and mountain"

Dates can be a specific day such as "October 12th".
Or day of the week like "Sunday".
Or "Today" or "Tomorrow".

After search resulted is found you can start a new search or say "Stop" to exit.

Sample search phrases.

 "Looking for billy ride on October 12th".
 " I want to ride Sunday"
 "Grizzly ride today"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
